        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 style="color:darkred">Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                1.34 million Australians aged over 50 were born overseas in a non English speaking country. Older people from Culturally and linguistically diverse (CALD) backgrounds with chronic diseases have a higher risk of mental health issues than those born in Australia.
                Our Mission is to help Elder people from CALD background about the stigma attached with mental health issues by raising awareness about its importance and educate them on how to access mental heath services by overcoming English as their barrier.
            </p>
        </div>
